    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, \"unruly crowds\" and \"agitators\"? that sounds a bit intense... i was hoping for something that felt a bit more like a news report on a movement. why did you choose words like 'unruly' or 'agitators' specifically? don't you think those might make it sound more like a riot than a protest?",
